short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Redirects all Satisfactory Fandom Wiki pages to Wiki.gg

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension redirects all requests for the Satisfactory Fandom Wiki to the non-obsolete Satisfactory Wiki.gg Wiki. 

Includes a toggle to allow temporarily disabling redirects if this is desired.
